<h2 class="bold font-l">"Ghost Capture"</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
&quot;Ghost Capture&quot; requires Sly to smash the coffin of the Evil Wolf Priestess to release the ghosts trapped with her. While Sly thinks it's a little cruel to do that to someone's corpse, Bentley emphasizes that she had Evil in her name. </p>
</div>
